      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَنْ حَلَفَ سِرّاً فَلْيَسْتَثْنِ سِرّاً وَ مَنْ حَلَفَ عَلاَنِيَةً فَلْيَسْتَثْنِ عَلاَنِيَةً\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4301 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Whoever takes an oath in private should make an exception in private, and whoever takes an oath publicly should make an exception publicly.\""
        ]
      }
    },
